OL,3,CHeathrow Airport sees record-breaking
OL,4,Cyear for annual passenger numbers
OL,6,FHeathrow Airport has reported its
OL,7,Fbusiest year ever, with 83.9 million
OL,8,Fpassengers passing through its
OL,9,Fterminals in 2024.
OL,11,FThe figure is 4.7 million higher than
OL,12,Fin 2023 and surpasses the previous
OL,13,Fannual record of 80.9 million set in
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FThe airport in west London expects
OL,17,Fpassenger numbers to rise further in
OL,18,F2025, forecasting 84.2 million
OL,19,Ftravelers over the coming year.
