OL,3,CHeathrow Airport sees record-breaking
OL,4,Cyear for annual passenger numbers
OL,6,FHeathrow's chief executive, Thomas
OL,7,FWoldbye, described 2024 as "an
OL,8,Fexciting and record-breaking year" and
OL,9,Fpraised staff and partners for their
OL,10,Fefforts.
OL,12,FHe said: "I'm proud of all my
OL,13,Fcolleagues and our partners who worked
OL,14,Fso hard to deliver great experiences
OL,15,Ffor more passengers than ever before.
OL,17,F"In 2025, our journey towards better
OL,18,Fvalue for our customers will continue
OL,19,Fby investing in the kind of facilities
OL,20,Four passengers and airlines are
OL,21,Flooking for.
